body_html: I don't know off the top of my head if TensorFlow is built with GCS support out of the box. cc: @gunan It might be necessary to build TensorFlow from source and enable that support when you run ./configure. This shouldn't be tensorboard related.

body: I don't know off the top of my head if TensorFlow is built with GCS support out of the box. cc: @gunan It might be necessary to build TensorFlow from source and enable that support when you run `./configure`. This shouldn't be tensorboard related.
